  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to investigate a possible reduction in pre-operative anxiety in
      patients undergoing major elective surgery, by providing multimedia information regarding the
      patient pathway to and from the Operating Theatre.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      To determine whether multimedia information reduces the level of pre-operative anxiety in
      patients undergoing major elective surgery. To evaluate the efficacy of a video, showing the
      patient pathway to and from the Operating Theatre, compared with standard information, a
      written leaflet, about the operating room experience and environment.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
