  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

        Adult patients undergoing major elective surgery, never previously undergoing surgery as an
        adult (&gt;18) and admitted to hospital at least one day before the scheduled surgery.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients unable to give consent.

          -  Patients not able to watch the video.

          -  Patients admitted the same day of the planned surgery.

          -  Patients not at the first experience of surgery as an adult (&gt;18).
      </textblock>
